(900432639,'Tyler','Gutierrez','2024-09-19','11:40','Alana Caldwell (AC), Aylin Dorsey (AD), Raelynn English (RE), Harmony Gardner (HG), Bianca Hodges (BH), Kenneth Huffman (KH), Oaklynn Mckay (OM), Wren Mullins (WM), Camila Newton (CN), Donovan Scott (DS), Julian Sexton (JS), Luke Stuart (LS), Steven Webb (SW), Kayleigh Wise (KW)','SW','       mankind, checked the improvements of those barbarians. The
