(900653976,'Dominick','Harmon','2019-03-05','16:20','Logan Bauer (LB), Mariana Dougherty (MD), Jordan Estes (JE), Tate Fischer (TF), Hugo Golden (HG), Sadie Hubbard (SH), Hadley Ochoa (HO), Kane Villanueva (KV), Victor Wise (VW)','SH','      Curved like a sea-shell--hushed as some rapt seer,
 
