(900246014,'Sofia','Mccarthy','2018-05-02','15:40','Ruth Boyd (RB), Apollo Dorsey (AD), Aiden Erickson (AE), Lucca Fleming (LF), Margot Hess (MH), Ophelia Humphrey (OH), Aidan Moran (AM), Hope Owens (HO), Solomon Rangel (SR), Maximiliano Todd (MT)','LD',' John gave the name of the driver, which, as I have not been able to
